{"tid":981559,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華爾街日報 :白宮曾要求國防部準備攻伊朗","createTime":"2019-01-14T11:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T12:01:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca9b897688bc63b2199556a0ba845845bcfe93c","tid":981559,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】與伊朗有關的武裝組織去年9月初發射3枚迫擊炮，打中美國駐伊拉克巴格達大使館附近地區，事件中沒有人受傷。《華爾街日報》周日報道，當時美國國安顧問博爾頓領導的國家安全委員會，曾要求國防部提供對付伊朗的軍事行動選項。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述前高級官員稱，有關要求令人震驚，因為博爾頓等人對攻擊伊朗一事是如此輕率，令人感到難以置信。國防部最終應要求設計一軍事選項，但未知最終有否交予白宮、特朗普是否得悉博爾頓的要求，和美國打擊伊朗的認真計劃當時是否已成形。<br />\n<br />\n（華爾街日報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190114/s00014/1547403185358/%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%9B%BE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%94%BB%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190114%2Fs00014%2F1547403185358%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%2594%25BB%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597&d=e3TO9ons5iEXHyTzMAd6wTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=8ff214e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190114%2Fs00014%2F1547403185358%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%2594%25BB%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597&h=7fcb8b6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190114/s00014/1547403185358/%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%9B%BE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%94%BB%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97</a>"},{"pid":"0f5fd96d9b985ab481dec8ef206375b4adcf7f6e","tid":981559,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re